tly slowed down assuming Kw = 40. We also show that the results of\nN-body simulations match statistical orbital distributions of close-in\nsuper-Earths.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Oct 2015 19:07:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-18"}
