training open cluster WDs and\ndisagreements in the cluster ages, wide DWDs may provide more reliable\nconstraints on the IFMR. Expanding this method to the many wide DWDs expected\nto be discovered by Gaia may transform our understanding of the IFMR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2015 01:51:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-16"}
